description:
AJCR-09 EMBROIDERED NET 3 PCS

By Pcs: 3 Pcs Shirt: Net Trouser: Twisted Silk Dupatta: Net Color: Green

Synonymous with palatial gardens that are alive with blooming florals in vibrant hues, this olive-green ensemble is an epitome of resplendence. The embroidered Peshwas, a glimpse of grace, is beautified with threadwork in the enchanting hues of crimson and beige, intricately detailed with gold zari amidst a cluster of gold sequins, glistening like morning mist on petals. The embroidered dupatta, mirroring the magnificence of the outfit, makes it a timeless ensemble, perfect for dreamy-dusk celebrations.
DESIGN DETAILS:

Embroidered front bodice with neckline & bodice hem on net
Embroidered back bodice with neckline & bodice hem on net
18 embroidered kalis for peshwas on net
4 meter embroidered border for hemline on net
Pair of embroidered sleeves with border on net
2.5 meter embroidered dupatta on net with 4 side borders
1.5 meter dyed wide width twisted silk for trouser
